<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 27 Mar 2024 12:21:10 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>驻菲律宾外国记者谴责中国涉嫌操纵视频</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/foreign-correspondents-philippines-condemn-china-over-claims-video-manipulation-2024-03-27/</link><description>驻马尼拉的外国记者周三驳斥了中国的说法，即菲律宾让记者篡改在南海补给任务期间拍摄的视频，使其看起来像“受害者”。</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Mar 2024 12:19:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/foreign-correspondents-philippines-condemn-china-over-claims-video-manipulation-2024-03-27/</guid></item><item><title>名誉扫地的前司法部长寻求改变韩国选举</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/disgraced-ex-justice-minister-seeks-shake-up-south-korea-election-2024-03-27/</link><description>由名誉扫地的前法务部长曹国发起的韩国小反对党已成为其两个主要政党在下个月的议会选举中获得多数席位的潜在最大破坏者。</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Mar 2024 11:52:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/disgraced-ex-justice-minister-seeks-shake-up-south-korea-election-2024-03-27/</guid></item><item><title>中国电动汽车制造商比亚迪的目标是年销量增长 20% - 消息人士</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinese-electric-vehicle-maker-byd-targets-20-jump-annual-sales-2024-03-27/</link><description>据三位知情人士透露，中国电动汽车制造商比亚迪设定了 2024 年销量目标 360 万辆，较去年破纪录的销量增长 20%。</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Mar 2024 11:15:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinese-electric-vehicle-maker-byd-targets-20-jump-annual-sales-2024-03-27/</guid></item><item><title>债券持有人团体“坚决反对”中国开发商世茂的债务重组提议</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/bondholder-group-firmly-opposes-china-developer-shimaos-debt-revamp-proposal-2024-03-27/</link><description>违约的中国开发商世茂集团的一群主要债券持有人周三表示，“坚决反对”该公司重组115亿美元离岸债务的提议，在房地产行业危机不断加深的情况下，这给该公司的前景蒙上阴影。</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Mar 2024 11:01:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/bondholder-group-firmly-opposes-china-developer-shimaos-debt-revamp-proposal-2024-03-27/</guid></item><item><title>中国习近平告诉荷兰首相切断供应链将导致对抗</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-xi-tells-dutch-pm-cutting-supply-chains-would-lead-confrontation-2024-03-27/</link><description>据中国官方媒体报道，中国国家主席习近平周三对荷兰首相马克·吕特表示，制造技术壁垒、切断供应链只会导致分裂和对抗。</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Mar 2024 10:42:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-xi-tells-dutch-pm-cutting-supply-chains-would-lead-confrontation-2024-03-27/</guid></item><item><title>英格兰银行加强对私募股权和银行估值的审查</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/bank-england-steps-up-scrutiny-private-equity-bank-valuations-2024-03-27/</link><description>路透伦敦3月27日 - 英国央行周三表示，正在更深入地研究不透明的私募股权行业带来的风险，以及为何英国主要银行的估值与国际同行相比“偏低”。</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Mar 2024 10:33:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/bank-england-steps-up-scrutiny-private-equity-bank-valuations-2024-03-27/</guid></item><item><title>巴基斯坦军方和文职官员将调查造成中国公民死亡的爆炸事件</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/pakistan-reviews-security-protocols-chinese-nationals-after-suicide-bombing-2024-03-27/</link><description>官员称，巴基斯坦总理周三呼吁军方和文职官员对导致五名中国工程师死亡的自杀式爆炸事件进行联合调查，同时审查其项目的安全安排。</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Mar 2024 10:08:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/pakistan-reviews-security-protocols-chinese-nationals-after-suicide-bombing-2024-03-27/</guid></item><item><title>早盘买盘：日本警告美元再次下跌</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-03-27/</link><description>迈克·多兰 (Mike Dolan) 对美国和全球市场未来一天的展望</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Mar 2024 10:04:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-03-27/</guid></item><item><title>由于需求不温不火，中国电动汽车制造商蔚来下调第一季度交付预期</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinese-ev-maker-nio-cuts-q1-deliveries-forecast-2024-03-27/</link><description>中国电动汽车制造商蔚来汽车周三下调了第一季度的交付预期，以应对中国需求放缓和价格战的问题。</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Mar 2024 09:38:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinese-ev-maker-nio-cuts-q1-deliveries-forecast-2024-03-27/</guid></item><item><title>随着人民币贬值，市场押注人民币将进一步贬值</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/yuan-skids-markets-bet-more-depreciation-is-store-2024-03-27/</link><description>中国的人民币正在下滑，市场参与者怀疑当局正在故意但缓慢地让人民币小幅贬值，以补充宽松的货币政策并支持出口。</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Mar 2024 08:24:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/yuan-skids-markets-bet-more-depreciation-is-store-2024-03-27/</guid></item><item><title>俄罗斯金矿因塌方风险而暂停大部分救援工作 - 塔斯社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/most-rescue-efforts-russian-gold-mine-have-been-suspended-due-risk-another-2024-03-27/</link><description>据俄罗斯国家通讯社塔斯社周三报道，俄罗斯远东一座金矿的大部分救援工作已暂停，3月18日，由于存在再次倒塌的风险，该金矿有13名矿工被困。</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Mar 2024 06:28:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/most-rescue-efforts-russian-gold-mine-have-been-suspended-due-risk-another-2024-03-27/</guid></item><item><title>独家：中国、阿联酋、土耳其加强银行审查，俄罗斯难以收取石油付款</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/russia-struggles-collect-oil-payments-china-uae-turkey-raise-bank-scrutiny-2024-03-27/</link><description>八位知情人士称，由于中国、土耳其和阿联酋的银行对美国的二级制裁变得更加谨慎，俄罗斯石油公司的原油和燃料付款面临长达几个月的延迟。</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Mar 2024 06:04:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/russia-struggles-collect-oil-payments-china-uae-turkey-raise-bank-scrutiny-2024-03-27/</guid></item><item><title>中国推动货币互换，加强货币合作</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-promote-currency-swaps-strengthen-monetary-cooperation-2024-03-27/</link><description>中国央行行长周三表示，中国央行将继续推动本币互换，加强与亚洲经济体的货币合作，维护地区金融稳定。</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Mar 2024 05:18:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-promote-currency-swaps-strengthen-monetary-cooperation-2024-03-27/</guid></item><item><title>消息人士称，中国碧桂园聘请克罗尔进行清算分析</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-country-garden-hires-kroll-carry-out-liquidation-analysis-sources-say-2024-03-27/</link><description>据三名消息人士透露，碧桂园已聘请克罗尔在 5 月中旬的法庭听证会之前进行清算分析，这家陷入困境的中国开发商正在推进其离岸债务重组计划。</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Mar 2024 04:52:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-country-garden-hires-kroll-carry-out-liquidation-analysis-sources-say-2024-03-27/</guid></item><item><title>随着投资减少，中国国家主席习近平在北京会见美国高管</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/chinas-president-xi-met-us-executives-academics-beijing-state-media-say-2024-03-27/</link><description>中国国家主席习近平周三在北京人民大会堂会见了美国商界领袖，政府正试图吸引外国投资者和国际公司，以确保新规定的影响。</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Mar 2024 03:13:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/chinas-president-xi-met-us-executives-academics-beijing-state-media-say-2024-03-27/</guid></item></channel></rss>